room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 12" by Seattle Escape Games in Seattle
room_description:
Framed for a crime you didn't commit, you are now locked away in Washington's maximum security prison and have a permanent residence - that's what a life sentence gets you... Rumors from other inmates say that years ago, one of the prisoners escaped from cell block 12 and was never caught. They say he vanished right out of his cell.
Are the rumors true? Did someone really break out? Can you find the secret path to freedom before your window of opportunity closes?
